{
  "name": "Call Lightning (ASE)",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/lightning/bolt-forked-large-blue-yellow.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Summon a&nbsp; storm cloud in the sky (which must be visible).&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Each turn you may call a<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> bolt of lightning to strike, each creature within </span><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">5 feet </strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">must make a&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">DEX savie.</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;A creature takes&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">3d10 lightning&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">damage on a failed save, or&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">half as much</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> damage on a successful one.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">The spell is more effective beneath an existing storm.</span></p>\n<p>See <a href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/call-lightning\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">D&amp;D Beyond</a> for details.</p>\n<p><strong>Higher Level.</strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th or higher level, the damage increases by 1d10 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This spell is automated.&nbsp; It will place a \"storm\" and create an item that can be used to infict the lightning damage.</p>",
